    avsColYear: 'Sannad', avsColStart: 'Qiimo bilowga', avsColDepr: 'Qiimo dhimis', avsColEnd: 'Qiimo dhamaadka', avsRegPctLabel:'Heerka qiimo-dhimista (%)', avsLifeLabel:'Cimriga faa\'iidada (sano)', avsScrapLabel:'Qiimaha haraaga (%)', avsRegTableHeader:'Jadwalka qiimo-dhimista toosan', avsCmpTableHeader:'Isbarbardhig: Canshuur vs. Xisaabtan', avsModeSkatt:'Canshuur', avsModeRegnskap:'Xisaabtan', avsModeCompare:'Isbarbardhig', avsCmpSkatt:'Canshuur (hoos u dhac)', avsCmpRegnskap:'Xisaabtan (toosan)', avsCmpDiff:'Farqi', avsTotal:'Wadarta', avsCmpNote:'Farqi togan = qiimo-dhimista xisaabtaneed way ka sarreysaa → dayn canshuur dib loo dhigay. Farqi taban = qiimo-dhimista canshuur way ka sarreysaa → hanti canshuur dib loo dhigay.', avsRegnskapInfo:'Qiimo-dhimista toosan sida sharciga xisaabtanka § 5-3. Hantida waxaa lagu qiimo-dhimiyaa si siman muddo cimriga la filayo.', avsIntroSkatt:'Qiimo-dhimista canshuur (hoos u dhac): hantida sanadkiiba waxaa laga jaraa boqolley go\'an oo qiimaha haray. Dooro kooxda nooca hantida.', avsIntroRegnskap:'Qiimo-dhimista xisaabtaneed sida <strong>sharciga xisaabtanka § 5-3</strong>: hantida joogtada ah ee cimri xaddidan leh waa in lagu qiimo-dhimiyaa qorshe macquul ah. Habka toosan wuxuu kharashka u qaybiyaa si siman.', avsIntroCompare:'Isbarbardhig qiimo-dhimista canshuureed ee hoos u dhaca iyo qiimo-dhimista xisaabtaneed ee toosan. Farqiga wuxuu muujinayaa farqiyaadka ku meel gaarka ah ee saameeya canshuurta dib loo dhigay.', avsCmpValTitle:'Qiimaha hantida', avsCmpBookVal:'Qiimaha buugga', avsCmpTaxVal:'Qiimaha canshuurta', avsCmpValDiff:'Farqi', avsCmpValNote:'Qiimaha buugga = qiimaha haraaga xisaabtaneed (qiimo-dhimis toosan). Qiimaha canshuurta = qiimaha hoos u dhaca. Farqi = buug − canshuur. Farqi togan → dayn canshuur dib loo dhigay. Farqi taban → hanti canshuur dib loo dhigay. Qiimayaashu waxay ku salaysan yihiin xogta isbarbardhiga kore.',
    avsCmpEffTitle:'Saamaynta canshuurta ee farqiyaadka ku meel gaarka ah', avsCmpEffDiff:'Farqi ku meel gaar ah', avsCmpEffTax:'Cashuur dib loo dhigay (22%)', avsCmpDebtShort:'deyn', avsCmpAssetShort:'hanti',
    avsIntroInfo: 'Dulmar kooban oo ku saabsan qiimo-dhimista xisaabaadka iyo canshuurta.', avsLawLink: 'sharciga canshuurta §§ 14-40 ilaa 14-48',
    avsInfoContent: '<div style="font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:12px;">Maxay tahay qiimo-dhimista?</div><div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--ink2);line-height:1.7;"><p style="margin:0 0 10px;">Qiimo-dhimista waxay ka dhigan tahay in qiimaha hantida joogtada ah (mashiinnada, gaadiidka, dhismayaasha) loo qaybsado muddada cimrigeeda — halkii laga kharash-gelin lahaa dhammaantii markii la iibsanayo.</p><p style="margin:0 0 10px;"><strong>Xisaabaad (sharciga xisaabaadka § 5-3)</strong><br>Qiimo-dhimista waxay ku dhacaysaa qorshe macquul ah. Habka toosan ayaa ugu caansan, laakiin habku waa inuu ka tarjumaa isticmaalka dhaqaale ee la filayo ee hantida.</p><p style="margin:0 0 10px;"><strong>Canshuur (sharciga canshuurta §§ 14-40 ilaa 14-48)</strong><br>Qiimo-dhimis hoos u dhac: boqolkiiba go\'an oo haraaga ah sannad kasta. Qiimo-dhimis sare bilowga, hoose waqtiga kadib. Heerku wuxuu ku xiran yahay kooxda qiimo-dhimista (a–j). Kooxda hantida lagu rido waxay <strong>saameyn weyn</strong> ku leedahay qaddarka jarista canshuurta — heer sare wuxuu ka dhigan yahay jaritaan dhakhso ah iyo canshuur hoose sannadaha hore. Marka haraagu hoos u dhaco 30,000 NOK, qaddarka oo dhan si toos ah ayaa loo jari karaa.</p><p style="margin:0 0 10px;"><strong>Maxaa farqi u ah?</strong><br>Sababtoo ah xeerarka canshuurta iyo xisaabaadku waxay u adeegaan ujeeddooyin kala duwan. Xeerarka canshuurtu waxay inta badan bixiyaan jaritaan dhakhso ah (dhiirigellin), halka xeerarka xisaabaadku ay raacaan qorshaha hoos u dhaca qiimaha dhabta ah. Farqigu wuxuu abuuraa <em>farqiyaad ku meel gaar ah</em> oo saameynaya canshuurta dib loo dhigay miisaaniyada.</p><p style="margin:0 0 10px;"><strong>Hanti vs. deyn canshuur oo dib loo dhigay</strong><br>Marka qiimo-dhimista canshuurtu ka badan tahay xisaabaadka → qiimaha buugaagta > qiimaha canshuurta → <span style="color:var(--red,#c44);">deyn canshuur oo dib loo dhigay</span>.<br>Marka xisaabaadku sare yahay → liddi → <span style="color:var(--green,#2a7);">hanti canshuur oo dib loo dhigay</span>.</p><p style="margin:0 0 10px;"><strong>Maxay canshuurta dib loo dhigay ka dhigan tahay dhab ahaantii?</strong><br>Waa ku saabsan <em>goorta</em> aad hesho jarista, maaha in aad hesho iyo in kale. Wadarta jaritaanku waxay caadi ahaan isku mid tahay waqtiga, laakiin waqtigu wuu kala duwan yahay.</p><p style="margin:0;opacity:.7;font-size:12px;">Isticmaal qaabka <strong>Is-barbar dhig</strong> si aad u aragto tirooyin gaar ah ee farqiga habaabyada dhexdooda.</p></div>',
